      <title>中国和美国需求放缓给星巴克前景蒙上阴影，星巴克股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-shares-tumble-china-us-demand-slowdown-clouds-outlook-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星巴克股价周三收盘前下跌近 14%，此前这家咖啡连锁店因美国消费者对通胀的疲软需求持续疲软以及中国经济复苏慢于预期而下调了年度预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-shares-tumble-china-us-demand-slowdown-clouds-outlook-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
